overview: Playing before one of the biggest crowds in their history, Pearl Jam ripped through their 12-song set at this landmark performance at the Pinkpop Festival in the Netherlands on June 8, 1992.  Setlist: Even Flow, Why Go (Rain), Jeremy, Deep, Alive, Black, Leash, Once, Porch, Pulled Up (Talking Heads cover), Suggestion (Fugazi cover), Rockinâ€™ in the Free World (Neil Young cover)
title: Pearl Jam: Live at Pinkpop 1992
